text: This place is located in the Peak District. There are a lot of options. Bought a bag here and very satisfied. The staff was really nice and willing to wait for me to choose. What a great person. The price is also very reasonable. I recommend this place.

A very nice shop to buy souvenirs in Singapore. We went there around Chinese New year and most of the stuff were available for just 2 SGD.. it's right across the street from China town point. Very convenient store and nice shop owner.
